</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D76EB69FF8FFFB2FF53F802FA523C58" blockId="13.[151,1436,1951,2031]" lastBlockId="14.[151,1436,151,378]" lastPageId="14" lastPageNumber="143" pageId="13" pageNumber="142">
13(12). Upper eye lobes wide, with at least 9 ommatidia........................................................... 14 - Upper eye lobes narrow, with 5–6 ommatidia. 
